{"article_id":"t7chV2PFv6LjItqF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New Jersey Gov . Chris Christie roared into Sunday after a fierce debate performance hours earlier","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"in which he slowed rising ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"fellow GOP presidential candidate Sen. Marco Rubio , with the New Hampshire primary ahead .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"\" He ' s a good guy ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"but he ' s just not ready to be president , \"","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Christie told \" Sunday , \"","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"after attacking Rubio for his inexperience","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"in running government .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" I felt justified","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"because I ' ve been saying this for a long time . \"","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Christie is one of three GOP candidates with governor experience","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"competing with Rubio for the so-called \" Republican establishment \" vote","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"and trying to stay alive in the race , with insurgents Donald Trump and Texas Sen. Ted Cruz also in the top tier .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"\" I am tested and prepared and ready , \"","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"said Christie ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"arguing","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that Barack Obama becoming president as a one-term senator , like Rubio , has been a disaster for the country .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" We don ' t need another on-the-job training , \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"\" I ' m glad","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"the American people saw","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"( Rubio ' s debate performance )","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"before they made another mistake . \"","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"In response to Christie ' s attacks at the ABC debate Saturday night in New Hampshire , Rubio , R-Fla. , stumbled and repeated himself several times about Obama ' s running the country .","depth":2},{"id":24,"text":"Ohio Gov . John Kasich ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"who like Christie is banking on a good showing in independent-minded New Hampshire ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"dismissed the notion","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"that he ' s competing with Christie and former Florida Gov . Jeb Bush for the establishment vote ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"despite having a career","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that includes 18 years in Congress .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"\" I am not an establishment candidate , \"","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"he told \" Sunday. \"","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"\" And I ' m not an anti-establishment candidate . \"","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"He cited his individual efforts","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to reform welfare and the Pentagon","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and repeated","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that his 2016 platform includes a \" path to legalization \" for illegal immigrants in the country ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"while also calling for the completion of a wall along the southern U.S. border .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"He also dismissed the notion","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that New Hampshire is do-or-die for his campaign .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" All","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"I have to do","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"is finish well , \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"\" I have the best ground game . \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Bush ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"who like Rubio is from Florida ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and was considered a mentor to the senator ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"on Sunday continued his efforts","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to move ahead of Rubio .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" The simple fact is , I ' m a leader , \"","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"he told \" Sunday. \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"\" Marco Rubio is a gifted speaker .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"But we ' re competing for president of the United States , not the back bench of the Senate . \"","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Trump was hit hard by Bush in the debate for his support of eminent domain ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"with Bush pointing out","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that Trump tried to take property for an `` elderly woman '' in Atlantic City for a casino parking lot .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"`` Shush , ''","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Trump said to Bush","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"as he tried to respond to the attack .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said several times Sunday","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that he thought","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"he won the debate .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"He also told","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that he has a \" good team \" in New Hampshire","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and called last week ' s Iowa Caucuses ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"in which he lost to Cruz ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"\" complicated . \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The billionaire businessman also suggested","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"he would like to challenge Democratic presidential candidate Vermont Sen. Bernie Sanders in the general election .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Trump suggested","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that Sanders , a self-described Democratic socialist , is perhaps a \" Communist . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":143,"left":94,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":81,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":74,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":78,"right":79,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":76,"right":77,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nucle